I am Ahmed Hagag (IEEE Mâ€™13). I received a B.Sc. (Honours) degree in pure mathematics and computer science from the Faculty of Science, Menoufia University, Egypt, in 2008, and an M.Sc. degree in computer science from the same university, in 2013.
